{"tid":562438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【幼女日記揭秘】爸爸戀上失散大女搞大肚 妹妹畫作揭亂倫","createTime":"2018-02-16T02:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T04:13:32.000Z","uid":122,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbd77527947773ad882e5390ac388f12b0a025e","tid":562438,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"美國維珍尼亞州一對夫婦年輕時「搞出人命」，無力撫養下只得將親生女兒送走。18年後，亭亭玉立的女兒回來相認，兩夫婦的關係卻開始一落千丈，最後丈夫無恥得拿11歲幼女的控訴日記供認自己搭上女兒並「搞出人命」，丈夫為迎娶大女更跟太太、即大女的媽媽離婚。<br />\n<br />\n現年42歲的普拉德（Steven Pladl）22歲那年與艾莉莎（Alyssa）珠胎暗結，那年艾莉莎才只有17歲。兩人的長女在1998年1月出生，身為未成年媽媽的艾莉莎不堪壓力，與普拉德決定將女兒送給人領養。兩口子在2006年拉埋天窗，再育有兩位女兒。<br />\n<br />\n這位女嬰獲領養後獲改名凱蒂（Katie），她在2015年8月首次聯絡普拉德及艾莉莎，並在2016年6月，即滿18歲不久，就前往維珍尼亞州與生父母見面。艾莉莎對於與親生女兒團聚，感到欣喜若狂，沒料卻「引狼入室」，夫婦關係從此變差。<br />\n<br />\n去年3月，普拉德與艾莉莎離婚。有日普拉德說要與艾莉莎談一談，並拿出11歲女兒的日記叫艾莉莎看，上面寫著：「凱蒂懷孕了。爸爸說他們感覺似一對。他們那晚是否有點太醉了？爸爸真的淫蕩。」另一段寫道：「爸爸說她（姐姐）的寶寶也是他的寶寶。是他令她懷孕嗎？爸爸甚至說她是我繼母，他媽的。他甚至不想我再叫她做姐姐了。凱蒂是我姐姐，但現在大概是他（爸爸）的妻子了。」<br />\n<br />\n艾莉莎相信，丈夫對自己與親生女兒亂倫一事難以啟齒，才叫她看11歲女兒的日記。艾莉莎憶述：「我失控了。我開始尖叫，感到要嘔了。」她續道：「我說，這就是你急著離婚的原因嗎？你要嘗試娶她？他答是。」兩父女後來還舉行婚禮，直至上月27日被捕，被控亂倫及通姦等罪名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes20.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes100.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes500.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes1000.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/ab/ea/20/abea20f0da5c34ad71b6e251c368e847.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fab%2Fea%2F20%2Fabea20f0da5c34ad71b6e251c368e847.jpg&h=16635c96&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"47c0e2683394bb4110d3bd0d74542c64e1081e9b","tid":562438,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1500b677642086cdfe401f0d8564c212c87c89e","tid":562438,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59001101eb45e0d1474a7333c5a06868b112fa0","tid":562438,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"反而想睇畫作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf978edfce553643c5315136de62d8349431b93","tid":562438,"uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180216/640_42d5d38970caeb9d2c83dcc4c1cae2b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180216%2F640_42d5d38970caeb9d2c83dcc4c1cae2b4.jpg&h=b662b591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普拉達長女福絲可變正妹，幼女日記揭爸爸亂倫授精懷孕。翻自《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180216/640_dd9016b7e74912ad71b4cf54366b84e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180216%2F640_dd9016b7e74912ad71b4cf54366b84e5.jpg&h=11ec054a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普拉達和福斯可後來還舉行婚禮，普拉達的母親、也就是福絲可的阿嬤(左)，以及福絲可的養父母(右方)都還來參加「婚禮」。翻自《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"6e4ced137b6960608b78138001f69e0ad86057d2","tid":562438,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:34:27.000Z","msg":"細女中文幾好"},{"pid":"00580826279c1f21f9d4b33e7dcf7af132544c2c","tid":562438,"uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"a59001101eb45e0d1474a7333c5a06868b112fa0","tid":562438,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:33:45.000Z","msg":"反而想睇畫作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180216/640_1211ca86e063578f47f73698f7dea481.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180216%2F640_1211ca86e063578f47f73698f7dea481.jpg&h=dee0bec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n普拉達的幼女、也是福絲可的妹妹，她的日記揭發這段亂倫，說爸爸是魔獸，生下的孩子會變成半人半獸。翻自《每日郵報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180216/640_b6691b8584ca84d76d91ce8578e6abcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180216%2F640_b6691b8584ca84d76d91ce8578e6abcf.jpg&h=167d7778&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福絲可生母艾莉莎。翻自《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"a5c358ed39873e5d9ec128cd821f50592d742cdc","tid":562438,"uid":65716,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:35:17.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"32afedb81299fae97240fd3c14a0ce684a4adccc","tid":562438,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"睇圖已知成日跪低含老豆"},{"pid":"748d7391d9d9c8132515f11c52da3d50340caa92","tid":562438,"uid":41922,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:38:58.000Z","msg":"老豆keep得幾型,個老婆肥撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c622098d528a62146c3d2217b6305a97500c8103","tid":562438,"uid":62409,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"咁好難怪個老竇"},{"pid":"df6fe44f50d1bc60f6750aabe3ddc967c082fe15","tid":562438,"uid":54228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:40:32.000Z","msg":"兩母女調轉就冇事發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60c9da9fef08936904488f8e0096fa168ad85c36","tid":562438,"uid":15309,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T02:41:42.000Z","msg":"遲下生多個女 又送出去<br />\n18年後又返黎相認啪啪啪 離婚再婚生女<br />\n無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c70ef57cdec54d30b87a868984b1c8988494173","tid":562438,"uid":138860,"lik